    <div xml:id="Aink73">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>vaṇṇa voṇṭaḻai nuṭaṅka vāliḻai</l>
<l>yoṇṇuta larivai paṇṇai pāynteṉak</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṟuṅ kuvaḷai nāṟit</l>
<l>taṇṇeṉ ṟiciṉē peruntuṟaip puṉalē.</l>

</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


<l> Because the young woman with bright forehead [and] choice jewels</l> 
<l> jumped into the tank(?), so that [her] colourful bright leaf[-skirt] swung: </l> 
<l> May waterlilies fragrant with nectar be fragrant! </l> 
<l> May the flood at the big ghat be cool! </l> 




</lg>
